{"hb4489a80g69bcg4500gbaffg10132dfc8e28": ["A fine night for it!", "c774d764-4a17-48dc-b470-32ace9ce447d", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntTieflingCelebration_CRD_Wyll.html", "d53696cf-5e31-a262-a0b3-3b63572fa165"], "h06cddc26g7136g4856g9bf4gcdd208df5f57": ["Such exquisite torture.", "c774d764-4a17-48dc-b470-32ace9ce447d", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntTieflingCelebration_CRD_Wyll.html", "69e50bea-3741-9ddd-3c3c-ce9555106631"], "h1a2f64c8g1822g4963g9f10g31893ba94897": ["Don't keep me waiting, I beg you.", "c774d764-4a17-48dc-b470-32ace9ce447d", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntTieflingCelebration_CRD_Wyll.html", "4249cdc1-7d9b-4727-795c-7a0903e3e93d"], "hd7c681ceg5fa5g4d9cga56cg2330fcc3e723": ["Cheers.", "c774d764-4a17-48dc-b470-32ace9ce447d", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntTieflingCelebration_CRD_Wyll.html", "7f160fc7-272d-6663-1e22-5677527460b6"], "h2df73045gd161g476cgae46gf1cdb660f7ae": ["Cheers!", "c774d764-4a17-48dc-b470-32ace9ce447d", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntTieflingCelebration_CRD_Wyll.html", "f8832dec-4b32-3d83-832d-fcd5ea05cf82"], "h2ee1840dg165cg4ee6gad32gf90c3a4ba4ac": ["A fine night for it!", "c774d764-4a17-48dc-b470-32ace9ce447d", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntTieflingCelebration_CRD_Wyll.html", "57e30d66-bb93-fb83-849f-c58d47fbe850"], "h73d795fbg53c6g453fg832fg2408e1fca747": ["Wyll, I'd like you to join me in my bunk tonight.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntTieflingCelebration_CRD_Wyll.html", "2d062ae2-5529-a6c9-6fcf-7942b425780e"], "hfa582f58gec4bg49d4g9bedg1579aabe1be2": ["I've thought about your offer, and I'm afraid I'm not interested.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntTieflingCelebration_CRD_Wyll.html", "bb8d4fb3-8d14-0439-34a0-a16030934c79"], "h7a061dabg26e4g49d8gae6ag2c71164e2a81": ["<i>Leave.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntTieflingCelebration_CRD_Wyll.html", "cfa7c906-6ced-a53c-6451-e36c70aca24b"], "h4fbfc469ga4f3g4b93g9dbbg760c7bf212af": ["There he is - the man himself. Let us raise a glass!", "c774d764-4a17-48dc-b470-32ace9ce447d", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntTieflingCelebration_CRD_Wyll.html", "793a9ed4-03b3-79d9-2d03-3c72f2d3b49f"], "hb2f7f36ag0396g426dga21fg181f0c6826e3": ["There she is - the woman herself. Let us raise a glass!", "c774d764-4a17-48dc-b470-32ace9ce447d", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntTieflingCelebration_CRD_Wyll.html", "793a9ed4-03b3-79d9-2d03-3c72f2d3b49f"], "ha05dcdbbg04aag4e68gbdc2ga3d8de497f4a": ["To freedom from tyranny! May we hew a clear path for the downtrodden to travel.", "c774d764-4a17-48dc-b470-32ace9ce447d", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntTieflingCelebration_CRD_Wyll.html", "4a89f78c-c7d9-d150-fe9d-e2d1d3da2ea2"], "hfd0800b9gd395g44dfga573g5d8ec471cd15": ["To you - a legend in the making.", "c774d764-4a17-48dc-b470-32ace9ce447d", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntTieflingCelebration_CRD_Wyll.html", "d22a3b30-aeb7-800e-6a00-5110cc326a19"], "h806ae6adg73dbg458dgaeccgc9be32f02e6a": ["And to the Blade! Another wrong righted, another page written!", "c774d764-4a17-48dc-b470-32ace9ce447d", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntTieflingCelebration_CRD_Wyll.html", "11dbb45b-a6e1-fdd8-bfbf-87a23f1799bc"], "h7c208de8ge586g4a2cgb78bg44b9edc21801": ["Wyll, I thought you might want to join me in my bunk tonight...", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntTieflingCelebration_CRD_Wyll.html", "baa9e2bb-c2fa-e672-793d-4fa412704072"], "h806b831eg841eg4603g9d67gf01f636e086b": ["Ah. Well. An intriguing offer, truly, but - I just don't feel that kind of connection.", "c774d764-4a17-48dc-b470-32ace9ce447d", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntTieflingCelebration_CRD_Wyll.html", "5e9f8eaa-61ce-36f3-f4b3-69df5755fe11"], "hd162f8bfgaf7eg4586gbe61gcf7db32f78fe": ["But consider me flattered. A boon for my ego.", "c774d764-4a17-48dc-b470-32ace9ce447d", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntTieflingCelebration_CRD_Wyll.html", "c73ecf96-4084-0d04-bfb2-6dcd2c6c77c0"], "h2bc8ab76g0d09g4b78gad95g6aeb05e31f91": ["'The Blade' would have very much failed on his own.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntTieflingCelebration_CRD_Wyll.html", "aa6254a7-4f8c-f000-8472-94ac680b5957"], "h42ee7b7bge68dg4f89g96edg8cdb9b135f20": ["Cheeky! But let's not sour the evening with talk of maybes and might-have-beens.", "c774d764-4a17-48dc-b470-32ace9ce447d", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntTieflingCelebration_CRD_Wyll.html", "aafdff34-88b4-264b-906d-a404169f18cc"], "hf8c38196gf214g454dgbd77g2544f2f5ca5a": ["Already, the bards are preparing their anthems, the poets their verses.", "c774d764-4a17-48dc-b470-32ace9ce447d", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntTieflingCelebration_CRD_Wyll.html", "5d94fcb5-0a6a-c735-c582-14497b346131"], "hfaaf693fg2ce3g48f4gb5bfg09edfe24caf6": ["Your name will be forever linked to the Blade of Frontiers. Could you have imagined such fortune a tenday ago?", "c774d764-4a17-48dc-b470-32ace9ce447d", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntTieflingCelebration_CRD_Wyll.html", "a6d00cba-c8a1-f435-50f5-b1aaa98935a7"], "h383e7135gcd3eg41acgb19ag592f1719783d": ["To fortune!", "c774d764-4a17-48dc-b470-32ace9ce447d", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntTieflingCelebration_CRD_Wyll.html", "9e232c2e-829a-3973-c4ee-4fae36a56d26"], "he6ba275eg97f1g4ea5gbc9cgeef7048cd5b6": ["To fortune!", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntTieflingCelebration_CRD_Wyll.html", "d3db4ba9-0416-3a22-a68f-b2b5da2ea30b"], "hb6c2181bgb486g4ab6g94d5gf4ab6fac3f5a": ["'Forever linked?' That isn't 'fortune' - that's a threat.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntTieflingCelebration_CRD_Wyll.html", "2ca40b45-f1ce-1d34-c4ea-b13eddafa366"], "hbe366bcegb276g4b31g91f8g5cba60132b15": ["Fuss all you want - this celebration is too sweet for you to sour it!", "c774d764-4a17-48dc-b470-32ace9ce447d", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntTieflingCelebration_CRD_Wyll.html", "fa1287ce-e962-88fc-b22d-35ecd8d8abba"], "hdad0a5e2g1bdbg4230gaffdg931d608f8bfa": ["Grab a tankard and suck down some ale. You've an edge in bad need of dulling.", "c774d764-4a17-48dc-b470-32ace9ce447d", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntTieflingCelebration_CRD_Wyll.html", "0b02d3a1-6bf7-d647-c69d-460e9e6e43b0"], "h420d6b5bged9ag4e60ga8f8g1a5facd31498": ["The Blade lives up to his myth!", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntTieflingCelebration_CRD_Wyll.html", "b4247caa-30ec-120c-e956-2d6402601b17"], "h82c49f09gbbd2g414bgba76g6ebc89c6cd40": ["Oh, but the Blade is no myth, chief. Myths are tall tales, fleeting as Cormyrian rain.", "c774d764-4a17-48dc-b470-32ace9ce447d", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntTieflingCelebration_CRD_Wyll.html", "8b18cbe9-dd9a-ba33-9b6d-8d04e44354cf"], "h27e8c9a0g7d07g4178g8d78g4daec318cb5f": ["I'm as real as the heart that beats in your chest. Now go off, have your fun.", "c774d764-4a17-48dc-b470-32ace9ce447d", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntTieflingCelebration_CRD_Wyll.html", "8283ee35-f1fd-70d0-14e0-5adb51e565eb"], "hc15c60c3g59beg40a0ga13dgc4507ed98dd5": ["I've got a tankard keeping me company.", "c774d764-4a17-48dc-b470-32ace9ce447d", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntTieflingCelebration_CRD_Wyll.html", "d8b1c232-4915-3ca8-59ea-ce29d3a7c21b"], "h5e55369eg823eg4ac3g92e3g5c22f5c5a9b2": ["We should really continue this conversation in my bed.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntTieflingCelebration_CRD_Wyll.html", "1a0e7966-4926-20bc-c8b1-21beabcbade5"], "he78d6ee8gc735g43d0g94ccgab1157af0397": ["Hmm - I'm not really feeling the connection.", "c774d764-4a17-48dc-b470-32ace9ce447d", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntTieflingCelebration_CRD_Wyll.html", "1a16ab3c-1e99-afa5-0113-e513b7b4615a"], "h71ff7ac3g9538g4dd2g82f2gf25b7e954e71": ["But consider me flattered. A boon for my ego.", "c774d764-4a17-48dc-b470-32ace9ce447d", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntTieflingCelebration_CRD_Wyll.html", "f92fd0a4-c6d3-9f6a-c175-490eb8fb075a"], "hf36c1d8dgef11g436bgb002g0f0ebe2fe968": ["And of course, to us.", "c774d764-4a17-48dc-b470-32ace9ce447d", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntTieflingCelebration_CRD_Wyll.html", "5dd1d3b3-9c84-6583-82c2-ac3dbe215dc9"], "he6a1d8dcg8cf0g4653gafb0gc1fad561378c": ["May our bond only grow stronger.", "c774d764-4a17-48dc-b470-32ace9ce447d", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntTieflingCelebration_CRD_Wyll.html", "bde9e0a6-c281-be02-7aa3-c0dc9123ebc2"], "h1ca1e400g17b9g492ag889fg6e1568b362cf": ["Hear! Hear!", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntTieflingCelebration_CRD_Wyll.html", "ab0458db-7be7-bd6c-9de5-ddd0531e93a7"], "h4852f597g08c7g416eg8331g6355a68adae2": ["Your heart beats strong, friend. The Blade rarely seeks partnership...", "c774d764-4a17-48dc-b470-32ace9ce447d", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntTieflingCelebration_CRD_Wyll.html", "b8b71466-6524-dace-da9d-5765595f01a8"], "h01ec4f33g9a59g4e2egbef2g10869d783b4d": ["... but the frontier provides few of life's creature comforts.", "c774d764-4a17-48dc-b470-32ace9ce447d", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntTieflingCelebration_CRD_Wyll.html", "a35bdb86-e108-6a20-71e4-6adca504a0ee"], "he94d3b01g9402g4a07ga950g9afecf2bbd06": ["I reckoned our union might extend to your bunk tonight.", "c774d764-4a17-48dc-b470-32ace9ce447d", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntTieflingCelebration_CRD_Wyll.html", "955d6ec1-e633-515c-f23f-23855e980275"], "h5c5efb5cg0bb0g495ag812fg833d1ed5fb66": ["I'd like that.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntTieflingCelebration_CRD_Wyll.html", "b14b992a-578a-46d8-00eb-9401d0a12207"], "h90672dd5g8741g4231g8186g70e0fefd3aac": ["Meet you at your bunk when you're ready.", "c774d764-4a17-48dc-b470-32ace9ce447d", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntTieflingCelebration_CRD_Wyll.html", "39d5ebcf-2f34-e682-0bf9-4a9029d60dc1"], "hc9159205g36b7g4009ga4d7gaad5a6a5c71b": ["Maybe another time.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntTieflingCelebration_CRD_Wyll.html", "e0a2fc24-bf25-f5f2-5dae-f9d5f1b3223c"], "hfb9f5726gd57dg40d4ga812gd4d9cc28996b": ["Of course, of course. Our future holds countless victories to celebrate.", "c774d764-4a17-48dc-b470-32ace9ce447d", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntTieflingCelebration_CRD_Wyll.html", "d9ae767d-d47a-2586-e423-7ad2f4e3f03c"], "hf3d55ff9g6110g4a3agabe8gca3588b97ac7": ["No. We're allies, nothing more.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntTieflingCelebration_CRD_Wyll.html", "ae6ad574-12be-3692-3759-5ccc6507b4d3"], "h4e2d3325g6710g41c8g8745gcfeb08242c6e": ["Of course, of course. Why complicate such a valuable friendship?", "c774d764-4a17-48dc-b470-32ace9ce447d", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntTieflingCelebration_CRD_Wyll.html", "df1167fb-c88a-e1f2-e2be-5ffd9053862f"], "hf23410abgb5ffg4b9cga2d2gba3cb92fb2b9": ["We should explore this bond in my bunk tonight.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntTieflingCelebration_CRD_Wyll.html", "e422eecf-6d41-b631-cd22-195b7717fc8b"], "h0bf79b18g719dg4ccfga0ebge34c552d6bf4": ["If I didn't know better, I'd think you were reading my mind.", "c774d764-4a17-48dc-b470-32ace9ce447d", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntTieflingCelebration_CRD_Wyll.html", "6384c19c-9425-5b2c-78f5-cb71bafead99"], "hffc10f19g9a81g429fg93cfg7d3b34cc975c": ["Meet you at your bunk when you're ready.", "c774d764-4a17-48dc-b470-32ace9ce447d", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntTieflingCelebration_CRD_Wyll.html", "999a03a7-d9b6-40ba-4c6a-a85a74ebc3fe"], "h9f0eb6ccg37cag411ag8a62gb565874186d6": ["I trust I won't have to wait long.", "c774d764-4a17-48dc-b470-32ace9ce447d", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntTieflingCelebration_CRD_Wyll.html", "53ae99ea-d1b8-a06b-d086-87aa70cc727a"], "h0f589741gc52dg4dd2g9b81g52dab3e40d40": ["Are you coming on to me?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntTieflingCelebration_CRD_Wyll.html", "07bb55ab-8c78-ec54-5375-f7a2909d952e"], "h17604c3ag854eg44aag970bgc324ec368ee7": ["I hadn't imagined myself so subtle. Or, to put it another way: yes.", "c774d764-4a17-48dc-b470-32ace9ce447d", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntTieflingCelebration_CRD_Wyll.html", "8503de20-b7c2-ab32-8bdf-a63835396413"], "hfa73ba25g98e6g48e2ga5cbg3c3873965b8c": ["Your heart beats strong, friend. The Blade rarely seeks partnership...", "c774d764-4a17-48dc-b470-32ace9ce447d", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntTieflingCelebration_CRD_Wyll.html", "670b343a-ea3b-41b8-4434-148c6dc1c9e5"], "habbb45c2g6ccbg42edgb1dbgb98df8f076ea": ["... but the frontier provides few of life's creature comforts.", "c774d764-4a17-48dc-b470-32ace9ce447d", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntTieflingCelebration_CRD_Wyll.html", "c0c0ae48-1de5-0da3-ca5b-13b8fc92fa1a"], "h224b3ae8g1522g4b5fgaf0ag2bd7c1a6efe5": ["I reckoned our union might extend to your bunk tonight.", "c774d764-4a17-48dc-b470-32ace9ce447d", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntTieflingCelebration_CRD_Wyll.html", "4b81ca67-3879-ac91-f7e0-300a5f8c27c3"], "h1479d78cg25a5g40e6g9a54g2cd1a6e74de9": ["We're only allies - and I'd like to keep it that way.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntTieflingCelebration_CRD_Wyll.html", "c5aed4af-5e11-a624-4798-d61ec9bc52fb"], "h7da3a984gf15bg495ega8dbge09caf2e791a": ["Of course, of course. Why complicate such a valuable partnership?", "c774d764-4a17-48dc-b470-32ace9ce447d", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntTieflingCelebration_CRD_Wyll.html", "afef4a3a-f25c-8018-b949-133554b8541b"], "hb18420c9gd180g420agb500g43abf8194945": ["<i>Leave.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntTieflingCelebration_CRD_Wyll.html", "8be1fb03-28d0-7e71-9c14-e6febeb77b94"], "hf082f5d1g1a81g4844gb7eag06dd0d89304f": ["And to you and Astarion. May your stars burn ever bright.", "c774d764-4a17-48dc-b470-32ace9ce447d", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntTieflingCelebration_CRD_Wyll.html", "ff7e2653-9bcf-a87b-ecc5-e722a2f7c5fa"], "h51b75879gf20dg4a21g90b4gdd6e9a69304c": ["Are you jealous?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntTieflingCelebration_CRD_Wyll.html", "f85eae3f-199d-874e-ec44-b4358be16215"], "h93633f97gd949g4721gbae1g711a0fe6c146": ["And if I were?", "c774d764-4a17-48dc-b470-32ace9ce447d", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntTieflingCelebration_CRD_Wyll.html", "1fef83ee-cbdf-dd53-50ff-7ee5f86fca08"], "haac7fec5ga20dg40e3g9217g3bc82c8c166a": ["I'd be flattered, honestly.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntTieflingCelebration_CRD_Wyll.html", "003bf7e9-cf64-5700-4975-2920a9453579"], "hd315d75agacafg4ab4gbbf3g66d0468064e6": ["Consider me jealous as a sisterless hag, then.", "c774d764-4a17-48dc-b470-32ace9ce447d", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntTieflingCelebration_CRD_Wyll.html", "e4143f83-56f7-0d91-8261-74ee1a398d5e"], "h8cb3a512gb487g4be4ga304gc53b1f4a527d": ["Eh - go off, have your fun. I've got a tankard keeping me company.", "c774d764-4a17-48dc-b470-32ace9ce447d", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntTieflingCelebration_CRD_Wyll.html", "34091cc1-3876-de19-8eb0-640b0fa3bb10"], "h24d5e916g0dabg4bf4ga784g82f70e668ef3": ["I'd enjoy watching you squirm.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntTieflingCelebration_CRD_Wyll.html", "645fa885-eb95-a9aa-d4dc-de685722b104"], "h9f98bbcdg3eabg4993gb842g412eaa2335a6": ["It's a good thing I'm not jealous then.", "c774d764-4a17-48dc-b470-32ace9ce447d", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntTieflingCelebration_CRD_Wyll.html", "c38022f8-a994-6aa1-dcf3-aeb0021beb34"], "h9ac1aab2gaf8dg4199gbb9egda771aab1c16": ["Go off, have your fun. I've got a tankard keeping <i>me</i> company!", "c774d764-4a17-48dc-b470-32ace9ce447d", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntTieflingCelebration_CRD_Wyll.html", "72165fd1-625e-6c27-fa62-eb964585d8ae"], "h4f5d7369gbe9fg42a9gad6agcd54b901b4c0": ["Cool your blood. I'm not interested in you like that.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntTieflingCelebration_CRD_Wyll.html", "028a565a-ea21-efcd-b874-ea7cc4e8a843"], "h71a71136g5a4dg429eg970cg40f7aff1aae1": ["It wouldn't matter one way or another.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntTieflingCelebration_CRD_Wyll.html", "f09ed418-1601-a72c-6c52-137231741183"], "h62f3e064gf214g4cbbg9548g0040f66520a9": ["My mind isn't entirely made up. Perhaps you might join me instead.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntTieflingCelebration_CRD_Wyll.html", "8ce84133-a8b5-4a66-2cc0-89e0501ee486"], "h8e0b1a05gfdf3g466dg80d8g612e51fa63f3": ["You do know how to set the Blade's heart all a-flutter.", "c774d764-4a17-48dc-b470-32ace9ce447d", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntTieflingCelebration_CRD_Wyll.html", "c22e6025-e2ae-b58e-e381-1b8241b66fa1"], "h8049febdg7613g423eg8d77g36021ed0b808": ["When the time comes to rest, just say the word and we'll meet at your bunk.", "c774d764-4a17-48dc-b470-32ace9ce447d", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntTieflingCelebration_CRD_Wyll.html", "e21a40ee-dc8d-4fbc-5caa-b135a6267afd"], "h967ee0e9g39c3g47e8gbc66g62ce23be62c2": ["Now go off, have your fun. I've got a tankard keeping me company.", "c774d764-4a17-48dc-b470-32ace9ce447d", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntTieflingCelebration_CRD_Wyll.html", "176098c9-61e2-dd77-0478-2fc6f1b95159"], "h96aee358gd940g42acg8b54g73f27e949e0d": ["Hear! Hear!", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntTieflingCelebration_CRD_Wyll.html", "74532913-3a3f-fd0c-7296-93abeee5f0d5"], "hf2f0c1f4gd192g488fga1a2g3b6450a0a8ce": ["Your heart beats strong, friend. I'm proud to fight at your side.", "c774d764-4a17-48dc-b470-32ace9ce447d", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntTieflingCelebration_CRD_Wyll.html", "19c81785-2140-05d5-928e-3fae875a6154"], "h241ceb1ag0917g4142ga076g919cf6921ad8": ["The Blade lives up to his myth!", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntTieflingCelebration_CRD_Wyll.html", "7db7e96d-13d1-ffba-7055-5b5adeea9017"], "hb84feb04ge762g4dbfg896ag3fb750928912": ["Oh, but the Blade is no myth, chief. Myths are tall tales, fleeting as Cormyrian rain.", "c774d764-4a17-48dc-b470-32ace9ce447d", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntTieflingCelebration_CRD_Wyll.html", "cafa178e-a70d-a6d3-4d49-6cfd973f5943"], "h7839461cg3794g4600gb972ge68798defb79": ["I'm as real as the heart that beats in your chest. Now go off, have your fun.", "c774d764-4a17-48dc-b470-32ace9ce447d", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntTieflingCelebration_CRD_Wyll.html", "664ae22d-12d6-00e7-a591-ab2b473ab331"], "h54be72cagd9bcg4c09g842ag51c6a77752e5": ["I've got a tankard keeping me company.", "c774d764-4a17-48dc-b470-32ace9ce447d", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntTieflingCelebration_CRD_Wyll.html", "9debd061-787f-7d83-e611-e5528c3c29ac"], "h4076eb6cg209ag4944gb457g6ee5589dbe37": ["You need to stay out of my business.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntTieflingCelebration_CRD_Wyll.html", "2364c7fb-a050-6cc6-3ec6-cc4297815835"], "h2dfb45a3ge683g4f23gbb63g74dd54435490": ["Your business is plain as a dread pirate's pikestaff, chief.", "c774d764-4a17-48dc-b470-32ace9ce447d", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntTieflingCelebration_CRD_Wyll.html", "46b11014-d4b5-5243-7b9d-1a15defbc4cf"], "h2fc848ecg37eeg4d45gb54agda598aad1d6d": ["And to you and Gale. May your stars burn ever bright.", "c774d764-4a17-48dc-b470-32ace9ce447d", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntTieflingCelebration_CRD_Wyll.html", "0f8d2b3d-51a8-0b6e-50cd-0a081ab3b172"], "hafada1afga264g45ddgb315g59eabe9b4fae": ["_", "c774d764-4a17-48dc-b470-32ace9ce447d", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntTieflingCelebration_CRD_Wyll.html", "eb91fcfd-6f90-edae-fcec-fa69bd2209e9"], "hee970a79g5db7g4fe7g9db5g465d26ea7de9": ["And to you and Karlach. May your stars burn ever bright.", "c774d764-4a17-48dc-b470-32ace9ce447d", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntTieflingCelebration_CRD_Wyll.html", "a7ee3b47-7dd5-30e0-d0ea-e22a5a0def7d"], "h7335e83cg2627g49a5gb03dg0a51c53a59f7": ["And to you and Lae'zel. May your stars burn ever bright.", "c774d764-4a17-48dc-b470-32ace9ce447d", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntTieflingCelebration_CRD_Wyll.html", "f53db11a-e813-4c7a-1a01-06b0502480eb"], "h0e7979e1g8c29g4bafg90b8g8018252dfd30": ["_", "c774d764-4a17-48dc-b470-32ace9ce447d", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntTieflingCelebration_CRD_Wyll.html", "555175f9-1176-4177-def2-ac394ab11923"], "h30379a08ge629g46bagaf03gcddadb371642": ["And to you and Shadowheart. May your stars burn ever bright.", "c774d764-4a17-48dc-b470-32ace9ce447d", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntTieflingCelebration_CRD_Wyll.html", "4c5ec7d9-af7d-96f1-43f6-f00479517b36"], "h6ab82bfag564cg4000ga39ag6b9c9c5b3b94": ["And to you and your paramour. May your stars burn ever bright.", "c774d764-4a17-48dc-b470-32ace9ce447d", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntTieflingCelebration_CRD_Wyll.html", "433b5d86-0807-d1ab-aa1f-07f6cb69ce8f"]}